{"tid":1955331,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港幾時先有網絡小說改編既電視劇睇","createTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T16:56:30.000Z","uid":236780,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a189251e93224d7b287ac312dc9eeb7298f67437","tid":1955331,"uid":236780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"好多國家都有<br />\n其實我地香港既高/連登既講故台都有唔同既小說<br />\n類型亦都5花8門<br />\n不過當然通常最吸引既都係愛情小說啦<br />\n我真係好想睇下D故變做電視劇<br />\n希望電視台可以同作者傾下版權翻拍<br />\n到時一定會有好大迴響<br />\n籃球故 宅女&gt;女神 無限告白<br />\n有一晚一個來電 未婚妻<br />\n波蘿包 等等<br />\n<br />\n你地點睇?"},{"pid":"b8c558d271955633363415213f52d192a043d5fc","tid":1955331,"uid":7343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"太多甜點做"},{"pid":"1981c5d14ffdae6479eca5c5bcc634b63c2280d5","tid":1955331,"uid":11185,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"向西聞記"},{"pid":"e8a4c476bfb73914a5d343d7ea98e72b7fe89440","tid":1955331,"uid":236780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8c558d271955633363415213f52d192a043d5fc","tid":1955331,"uid":7343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"太多甜點做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"有純愛故架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd56dec9d0f905c206675d6dcf36fe1405f8021b","tid":1955331,"uid":155246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"BL<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4133e46c661afcbcca00ac15050ab50d425eab3","tid":1955331,"uid":100772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:07:29.000Z","msg":"紅Van"},{"pid":"4fa4d7adaefd7b759d1c43e465cfee303e8cf849","tid":1955331,"uid":128616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T12:07:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8257506e63037cf15ae6cfa92e645f403c0b7bc","tid":19